## 결과 예시

[Security Headers]
Content-Security-Policy: Missing
Strict-Transport-Security: Missing

[CORS]
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

[Cookies]
Secure: Missing
HttpOnly: Present

[Summary]
Risk Level: High

